    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is a total gem\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, so it's in absolutely immaculate shape. No scratches, no dents, just pure driving bliss. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
