    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age and stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-floor brilliance. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are pristine without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and retains its original scent, showing no bolster wear or creasing. All interior electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function with tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a full documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the car drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a brand-new machine. This is a rare, investment-grade example perfect for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
